"""
adding Gaussing distribution to anti proton data array
"""

import numpy as np
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import statistics
from numpy import array
import pandas as pd
import random
pd.set_option('display.float_format', lambda x: '%0.4f' % x)

data = []

"""
Read data from total data file
--------------------
"""
print("Reading data ...")
data = array(pd.read_table("/Users/jiancheng/GRAMS/Toy Model/data/cut/TOF_anti_proton_1e7_0_500_0_4_result.txt", delimiter=" "))
print("finish reading data!")

print(type(data[1, 0]))
print(type(data))
print(data)

sigma = 0.3    #energy resolution percentage
deltaT = 0    #timing resolution/ns

time_pbar_err = np.array([None] * len(data[:,0]))
dEOut_pbar_err = np.array([None] * len(data[:,0]))
dEIn_pbar_err = np.array([None] * len(data[:,0]))

for i in range(len(data[:,0])):
    dEOut_pbar_err[i] = random.gauss(data[i, 0], sigma * data[i, 0])
    dEIn_pbar_err[i] = random.gauss(data[i, 1], sigma * data[i, 1])
    time_pbar_err[i] = data[i, 2] + deltaT * 2 * (random.random() - 0.5)
    print("applying error:"+str(int(100*i/len(data[:,0])))+"%", end='\r')

plt.scatter(time_pbar_err, dEOut_pbar_err, marker = '.', color = 'b', label = 'TOF out layer')
plt.scatter(time_pbar_err, dEIn_pbar_err, marker = '.', color = 'r', label = 'TOF inner layer')
plt.title('anti proton TOF with error')
plt.xlabel('Time [ns]')
plt.ylabel('Energy diposit')
plt.legend(loc='lower right')
#plt.axis([0, 20, 0, 10])
plt.grid(alpha = 0.2)
plt.show()

"""
adding Gaussing distribution to anti He3 data array
"""

import numpy as np
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import statistics
from numpy import array
import pandas as pd
import random

data = []

"""
Read data from total data file
--------------------
"""
print("Reading data ...")
data = array(pd.read_table("/Users/jiancheng/GRAMS/Toy Model/data/cut/TOF_anti_He3_1e7_0_1500_0_4_result.txt", delimiter=" "))
print("finish reading data!")

print(data[:, 0])
print(data[:, 1])
print(data[:, 2])
sigma = 0.3    #energy resolution percentage
deltaT = 0    #timing resolution/ns

time_He3bar_err = np.array([None] * len(data[:,0]))
dEOut_He3bar_err = np.array([None] * len(data[:,0]))
dEIn_He3bar_err = np.array([None] * len(data[:,0]))

for i in range(len(data[:,0])):
    dEOut_He3bar_err[i] = random.gauss(data[i, 0], sigma * data[i, 0])
    dEIn_He3bar_err[i] = random.gauss(data[i, 1], sigma * data[i, 1])
    time_He3bar_err[i] = data[i, 2] + deltaT * 2 * (random.random() - 0.5)
    print("applying error:"+str(int(100*i/len(data[:,0])))+"%", end='\r')

plt.scatter(time_He3bar_err, dEOut_He3bar_err, marker = '.', color = 'b', label = 'TOF out layer')
plt.scatter(time_He3bar_err, dEIn_He3bar_err, marker = '.', color = 'r', label = 'TOF inner layer')

start_time = 6
for n in range(14):
    plt.cla()
    plt.scatter(dEOut_He3bar_err[np.logical_and(time_He3bar_err > start_time+n, time_He3bar_err < start_time + 1 +n)] , dEIn_He3bar_err[np.logical_and(time_He3bar_err >start_time+n, time_He3bar_err <start_time + 1 +n)], label = "anti He3 45 degree", marker = '.', color = 'limegreen')
    plt.scatter(dEOut_pbar_err[np.logical_and(time_pbar_err>start_time+n, time_pbar_err<start_time + 1 +n)], dEIn_pbar_err[np.logical_and(time_pbar_err>start_time+n, time_pbar_err<start_time + 1 +n)], label = "anti proton 45 degree", marker = '.', color = 'royalblue')
    #plt.scatter(dEOut_dbar_err[np.logical_and(time_dbar_err>start_time+n, time_dbar_err<start_time + 1 +n)], dEIn_dbar_err[np.logical_and(time_dbar_err>start_time+n, time_dbar_err<start_time + 1 +n)], label = "anti deuteron 45 degree", marker = '.', color = 'lightcoral')
    plt.grid(alpha = 0.2)
